<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <title>Timer</title>
    <script>
        function setClientTime() {
            var currentTime = new Date();
            var hours = currentTime.getHours();
            var minutes = currentTime.getMinutes();
            var seconds = currentTime.getSeconds();
            if (minutes < 10)
                minutes = '0' + minutes;
            if (seconds < 10)
                seconds = '0' + seconds;
            document.getElementById('ClientTime').innerHTML = hours + ':' + minutes + ':' + seconds;
        }
        function refresh() {
            location.reload();
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body onload='setInterval(function(){refresh()}, ${refreshPeriod} ); setClientTime();'>
<p>Client time: <span id='ClientTime'></span></p>
<p>Server time: ${serverTime}</p>
<p>Server time: ${message}</p>
<p>User Id: ${user.getId()}</p>
<p>User Name: ${user.getUsername()}</p>
<p></p>
<p>Информация о сессии:</p>
<p>Session sessionId: ${session.getAttribute("sessionId")}</p>
<p>Session getId: ${session.getId()}</p>
<p><a href="exit">Выход</a></p>
</body>
</html>